    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a special tax deduction for employee training expenses that are: (1) also deductible as an ordinary and necessary business expense; (2) incurred under the National Apprenticeship Act or under a recognized State program; and (3) at least one percent of the total yearly wages paid by the employer claiming a deduction."
